  "body": "# Problem\r\n\r\nThrough the PR https://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/pull/16710, Noticed that we use the `quo/menu-item` component for drawer actions. From [Figma](https://www.figma.com/file/PPWkgOYlZZDxZv5SDGsZVV/Posts-%26-Attachments-for-Mobile?type=design&node-id=3425%3A413530&mode=design&t=eujxwMUXOjs9Aazc-1), we can infer that we should use `quo/action-drawer` component.\r\n\r\nSo, we have to replace the `quo/menu-item` component usage with the `quo/action-drawer` component.\r\n\r\nThere are two usages in our codebase: \r\n\r\n1. `src/status_im2/common/mute_drawer/view.cljs`\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/blob/2317e856bf351457d17435411fd1896b02f1cb81/src/status_im2/common/mute_drawer/view.cljs\r\n\r\n2. `src/status_im2/contexts/chat/messages/drawers/view.cljs`\r\n\r\nhttps://github.com/status-im/status-mobile/blob/2317e856bf351457d17435411fd1896b02f1cb81/src/status_im2/contexts/chat/messages/drawers/view.cljs\r\n\r\n### Notes\r\n\r\nRefer to the design team if needed.\r\n",
